{"tid":1181479,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"求其義賣音樂會","createTime":"2019-06-01T15:51:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T19:03:16.000Z","uid":237487,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b09d742ddecd9d891bcd5e1f195a66ecea6dd081","tid":1181479,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T15:51:58.000Z","msg":"聽聞ttn搞show 隊日本大band臨時話no show 就成個tour取消左， 主辦單位所有野硬食， 損失6 位數字， 求求大家幫幫手，推一推， 大家enjoy一下本地音樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ALKCZ0d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FALKCZ0d.png&h=095f9613&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「Show Must Go On」求其義賣音樂會<br />\n<br />\n月前，本地日系音樂主辦單位Neon Lit Music聯同TTN夥伴許仲和（阿和）開始密鑼緊鼓，為香港樂迷籌備大家期待已久的日本當紅樂隊香港站演出。期間，為滿足藝人鉅細無遺的技術要求和龐大訪港團隊，主辦單位付出巨款以期演出順利。<br />\n<br />\n然而，一向了解當事人的都會知道，無論Neon Lit Music或阿和都沒有金主撐腰，必須承擔一切開支。剛剛今天，最不幸的事情發生了，樂隊管理公司單方面取消演出。<br />\n<br />\n與其面對明天空無一人的場館，還有沉重得窒息的各種待償開銷。TTN和一眾本地獨立音樂藝人、策展人決定盡最後努力善用無法退款的場館，舉行「Show Must Go On」求其義賣音樂會，現召集本地藝術家、音樂人明天在Music Zone售出自己的存貨，並將收益連同門票收入全數捐予主辦方。<br />\n<br />\n此外，是次邀請演出的音樂單位，皆不收取任何演出費用全力支持活動，幫助NLM、阿和渡過難關。TTN廣邀大家踴躍參與，欣賞這場迷你音樂節級表演，還有在眾多稀有貨品中尋寶。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n鳴謝以下所有表演單位 Performing Artists: <br />\nSerrini<br />\n話梅鹿 - Prune Deer<br />\nMUKZI 木子 + The Island<br />\nTwisterella*<br />\nThe Ancient Mental<br />\nK'scope / 萬花筒<br />\nSugar Bro<br />\nstereo is the answer<br />\nUnto The Dawn<br />\nDeepInside<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n日期 Date: 02 June 2019<br />\n時間 Time: 7-11PM<br />\n地點 Venue: Music Zone - KITEC<br />\n(1 Trademart Drive, Kowloon Bay, Hong Kong)<br />\n入場費Entrance Fee:<br />\nHKD$280<br />\n<br />\n網上購票 Online Ticketing：<br />\nTickcat<br />\n<a href=\"http://tickcats.co/ticket/showmustgoon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftickcats.co%2Fticket%2Fshowmustgoon&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTpBhszO9bAnYmyMPTpIehd8%3D&h=b6b5b277\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">tickcats.co/ticket/showmustgoon</a><br />\n<br />\n活動詳情：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/303784170545032/?ti=ia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F303784170545032%2F%3Fti%3Dia&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTpBhszO9bAnYmyMPTpIehd8%3D&h=bcbb9538\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/303784170545032/?ti=ia</a><br />\n0<br />\n0"},{"pid":"04be27cf5f6091b08cc26f9fc0c1ffb7b40c6749","tid":1181479,"uid":4203,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T15:53:01.000Z","msg":"正 幾隊都想睇 Serrini 木子 話梅"},{"pid":"50d9ad2a9bcf17e48789f18e44fa46216e55264c","tid":1181479,"uid":66048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T16:37:15.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a212cc245b91f6bf51746f09a084fb178d3e7f","tid":1181479,"uid":59517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T18:28:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf665f57c9106e4dc60d63d924ef4ff77227ea4a","tid":1181479,"uid":33734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T19:43:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"493313fd485da8e00fe87abd2106ec35cda6fe97","tid":1181479,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04be27cf5f6091b08cc26f9fc0c1ffb7b40c6749","tid":1181479,"uid":4203,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T15:53:01.000Z","msg":"正 幾隊都想睇 Serrini 木子 話梅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T01:09:02.000Z","msg":"我都好鍾意話梅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e90d640ed81c23e